{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"34f348e083","title":"日记二十四则","origin":"中共武汉大学社会主义思想教育办公室编《武汉大学右派言论汇编(二)》, 1957年12月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"183bd2dfb1","index":0,"year":1956,"month":8,"day":20,"articleId":"34f348e083"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"94bea1b677","name":"查启林"},{"id":"d138cdec49","name":"武汉大学图书馆系学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"40e67e46f4","type":"title","text":"日记二十四则","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"e349fabfea","type":"authors","text":"武汉大学图书馆系学生查启林","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"e009eff68c","type":"subtitle","text":"一\t唐多令","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"06b99ee25b","type":"paragraph","text":"花香春至，岑头梅争开。严冬重来，冰河结冻阻中流，在何日、始还舟！","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"54e5e39bef","type":"paragraph","text":"一跃三千丈，跳过对岸头。定神看，不堪回首。目瞻四野尽方洲，出蛇穴、入虎口。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"96051309e7","type":"subtitle","text":"二\t生命是最不值钱的东西","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"7b2256c55d","type":"paragraph","text":"生命是最不值钱的东西，因为随时都可以死去。它的宝贵是人为的加工上面，是“道义”叫人活下去的。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"ff0d22caf8","type":"subtitle","text":"三\t最痛苦的是不信任","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"8a5a905b73","type":"paragraph","text":"感到人生最痛苦的是不信任，当你满肚子的衷心话向他倾吐，而使他无动于衷，这有何趣？然还好一点。最可怕的却还有暗的讥笑、毁谤、种种骇骇不忍入耳听起来是令人伤心已极。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"4f7fcc7a98","type":"subtitle","text":"四\t“高利贷”何曾算得清","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"91efd22ea0","type":"paragraph","text":"记主，不要再“欠债”，日积日累的是叫人还不清的，况且还要手续费等的这一翻的“高利贷”何曾算得清！","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"ee7eeec983","type":"subtitle","text":"五\t夜","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"1257c7cadc","type":"paragraph","text":"夜啊！秋天的夜，是因为面临深秋，就是寒冬了，虫在忧愁的叫，“促织”也不能成布过冬。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"8c17e0aefd","type":"paragraph","text":"他唯一的希望——还有一个小阳春。依篱残菊，那经得过严霜，满花飞舞，那把你放在眼上。孤株唯独立，落得有花无叶。赤祼祼，成什么样！春一来，百花齐宠。冬一到，万物皆殃。人在得意之中万般好，得/失意之时，条条路不通。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"52b9383821","type":"subtitle","text":"六\t一叶扁舟","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"fcb5438a31","type":"paragraph","text":"架一叶扁舟，落帆丢舵，飘在长流的水面上，随波逐浪，驶向那渺茫的旅途，无边无际，头顶穷庐、脚不踏地、随水向东流……。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"6761529b29","type":"subtitle","text":"七\t人怕死而活","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"baa7f7b5d9","type":"paragraph","text":"人为死而生，怕死而活。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"4c3bb38eb0","type":"subtitle","text":"八\t人有二个特征","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"c461823e9e","type":"paragraph","text":"人有二个特征——自私和取巧。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"c429fdc154","type":"subtitle","text":"九\t命运是上帝安排的","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"5035274fc9","type":"paragraph","text":"生活走在歧途，命运是上帝安排的。驱使着、命令着人们去波奔、探求、碰壁、回头……。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"e8efd1fad0","type":"subtitle","text":"十\t“喊打喊杀的蚊声”","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"b05227c07c","type":"paragraph","text":"……喊打喊杀的蚊声，向人猛烈攻击。汗水把我和床缚在一起。我没有力量和这些小小的蚊子搏斗，我仅有的一点点血，让它吸尽吧！","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"6e94fe4094","type":"paragraph","text":"贪婪无厌的东西，竟是如此大胆地饱吸又饱吸，我狠狠的打击它，然而我的手是重重地落在我的身上，挨痛的还是我。我呆不下去了我企图离开这里，我终于逃出了这里。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"4fa0009446","type":"paragraph","text":"我仿佛进入了另一个世界、朦胧的弯月，虽不甚明，照在大地上青的山，绿的草，纷白的墙、红色的屋顶。……","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"8ebce37c13","type":"subtitle","text":"十一\t“生活是一所没有狱卒的大笼”","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"72c21bbbec","type":"paragraph","text":"生活是一所没有狱卒的大牢笼，安分者每天可以求平安的二顿饭。通过栏棚。还可以重见青天(或者不可能)，只看得见门缝里射进来的阳光(或者不可能)可是只要你掘个洞逃亡夭夭，就有广阔的天地。会看见盛开的花，自由的写……幸福的暂时满足。有着愉快，纵有风雨的摧残。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"e2baa46249","type":"subtitle","text":"十二\t“社会上主要矛盾是自私”","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"877a49d3d7","type":"paragraph","text":"社会上的主要矛盾都是自私。因为自私各不相让，因为各不相让才有斗争。无论个人、社会、阶级、同学皆如此。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"bc933be43b","type":"subtitle","text":"十三\t“不媚其何能让你立足”","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"22962e92c0","type":"paragraph","text":"看样子吹牛拍马，献媚自己宠还很适合。因为这样很迎合某些“人物”的兴趣，不媚其何能让你立足，Q一事可证也。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"7e5e4c61bb","type":"paragraph","text":" (约56年8 20日以前写)","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"c8d0f00aad","type":"subtitle","text":"十四\t“巴上斯下都是人”社会主义制度","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"b255b3833b","type":"paragraph","text":"万物有时人有运，得意之时喜逢丢，","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"a6bc76349e","type":"paragraph","text":"乐人不知愁人苦。强人总把弱人欺。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"40013a9b0b","type":"paragraph","text":"快哉乐哉忘了形。苦哉愁哉伤死神，","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"2f25dae3cb","type":"paragraph","text":"快哉公道安何有？巴上欺下都是人。(56年4.11)","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"f35c148ce3","type":"subtitle","text":"十五 要坏就坏到底(56.10.19)","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"6b6450311c","type":"paragraph","text":"要坏就坏到底。就象行驶在大海中的无帆之船，飘入孤岛，土人则会把你当作外人看待的。转变就是屈膝，屈膝就得使人支配，支配之下必须服从。何谓也！","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"854fb2aa51","type":"subtitle","text":"十六\t真理不止一个","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"633dbb7593","type":"paragraph","text":"真理就是人的理性。一个人就有一个人的理性，真理也就不止一个。","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"3c21c1a35f","type":"subtitle","text":"十七\t挺受人世间的摆布和折磨","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"0b775a89c5","type":"paragraph","text":"不知在上天作了什么罪恶，刀杀、棍打一刻之痛，","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"2cbf859217","type":"paragraph","text":"被上帝贬责下凡。苦磨、刑拷身躯之残。","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"7f961d707c","type":"paragraph","text":"挺受人世间的摆布、折磨，心头之苦，无伤之苦，","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"b1a6db8546","type":"paragraph","text":"看穿乱赵的幻境畸形。更胜那枪杀苦刑。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"b6ef0b455a","type":"subtitle","text":"十八\t人与人之间关系是假面具","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"32ca22b99d","type":"paragraph","text":"人与人之间的相处，总是带着假面具，我咀咒，但我也不能不合污。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"40a9b254e4","type":"subtitle","text":"十九\t真是体无完肤了","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"901e59c427","type":"paragraph","text":"我是体无完肤了！这除了肉体的还有心灵的。南无大慈大悲啊！救一救多苦多难的弟子！","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"7418f28582","type":"subtitle","text":"二十\t世界上有两种人","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"3a75f19763","type":"paragraph","text":"世界上只有二种人，而这二种人都是危险的。叫的狗不咬人，然而他会骗人，不叫的狗是阴着咬人的。","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"a08783dd53","type":"subtitle","text":"二十一\t有人在监视我","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"5834809f1d","type":"paragraph","text":"一举一动一言行都有人在监视你的。这些好功者！这些无能落于妬嫉者！","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"17a76c8824","type":"subtitle","text":"二十二\t叹菊","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"775a98c99c","type":"paragraph","text":"独立寒秋，寄居篱下，","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"cdfcfcfa2b","type":"paragraph","text":"含悲装笑，叹孤苦零仃，","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"bc0e17e87f","type":"paragraph","text":"谁个见怜？骨节不硬，","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"903cd9c6a1","type":"paragraph","text":"根底非深，无能为力，","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"808ef93003","type":"paragraph","text":"何敢强行？岂能与晴令抗争！","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"101c6917e6","type":"paragraph","text":"休了罢！称一时英雄，","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"7a19c2c8d4","type":"paragraph","text":"座落何名？！寒露无面无情，","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"51b0c17605","type":"paragraph","text":"况晚风吹来更严峻，岂可能久有？","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"9cbd7ae17b","type":"paragraph","text":"晚秋深处，落花呜咽，","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"22ba12cad1","type":"paragraph","text":"一夜秋雨，残骸无存，","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"f5715d07c1","type":"paragraph","text":"再欢天色，鹅毛飞飘冬至也。","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"dab3fb17a8","type":"paragraph","text":"这时节，纵我遍天下，","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"d9848a3920","type":"paragraph","text":"菊无一存！","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"bfb4b5e87f","type":"subtitle","text":"二十三\t 落枫","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"6288a9a7ff","type":"paragraph","text":"是风在调笑她么？赶得漫天飞舞，弄得脸儿绯红，一个个跟着追踪，满天布的尽是情网。","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"f25df929f9","type":"subtitle","text":"二十四  灵魂是什么？","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"d0e30c0361","type":"paragraph","text":"灵魂是什么？我在知道，应当是一颗冰冻的心和一付破裂了的胆，没有野心，没有雄劲，不必去征服人。它已经没有了任何容量。","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"},{"id":"5f590f771b","type":"appellation","text":"(以上24篇日记标题都是编者所加的)","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083"}],"page":{"id":"dd156b7ff9","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34f348e083","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}